    <body>
        <div xml:id="NA390-kiḷavi">
            <p type="edition">1. itu pāṅkāyiṉa vāyil (ET: vāyilkaḷ) kēṭpa neruṅkic colliyatu.
                2. talaimakaḷ tōḻikku uraippāḷāy vāyilāka pukkāl kēṭpac colliyatūumām.</p>
            <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">1. This is what was said towards the mediator, who was [his] companion, so that he could hear. 
                2. It is also what SHE said as one talking to the confidante when a mediator had entered so that he could hear.</p>
            </div>
      <div xml:id="NA390">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            vāḷai vāḷiṟ piṟaḻa nāḷum</l>
<l>            poykai nīrnāy vaikutuyi lēṟkuṅ</l>
<l>            kaivaṇ kiḷḷi veṇṇi cūḻnta</l>
<l>            vayalveḷ ḷāmpa luruva neṟittaḻai</l>
<l>            yaitaka lalku laṇipeṟat taii</l>
<l>            viḻaviṟ celīiyar vēṇṭu maṉṉō</l>
<l>            yāṇa rūraṉ kāṇuna ṉāyiṉ</l>
<l>            varaiyā maiyō varitē varaiyiṉ</l>
<l>            varaipōl yāṉai vāymoḻi muṭiyaṉ</l>
<l>            varaivēy puraiyu naṟṟō</l>
<l>            ḷaḷiya tōḻi tolaiyuna palavē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>            It will be necessary indeed to go to the festival,</l>
<l rend="indent">            fastening for adornment’s sake to the wonderful broad hips</l>
<l rend="indent">            foliage [and] beautiful calyxes of white waterlilies from the paddy fields</l>
<l rend="indent2">            that surround Veṇṇi of Kiḷḷi, generous of hand,</l>
<l rend="indent3">            where the otter awakens from the sleep he keeps by the pond,</l>
<l rend="indent4">            daily, while sword-like Vāḷai fish are leaping?</l>
<l rend="indent">            If the man from the fertile village sees [us],</l>
<l>        not to marry [us will be] difficult.</l>
<l rend="indent4">            If he marries [us],</l>
<l>        many [will be] the good shoulders that are defeated, friend,</l>
<l rend="indent">            pitiable ones that resemble the bamboo on the mountain</l>
<l rend="indent2">            of Muṭiyaṉ with true words [and] mountain-like elephants.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
